<b>Answer:</b>  Are you planning on going all the way to 60? If so you should probably max your STA on creation since it is the hardest stat to raise with gear.  If not then get your STA above 100, you are unaffected by fatigue except that you will not be able to jump. If your STA is below 100, you will lose STR and AGI if you are fatigued. The reason to raise STA over 100 is that you get roughly 3hp for each point of stamina at you gain at higher levels.  HP are an important stat at higher levels. <br>
