<br>
<b>Answer:</b>  Evade isnt a skill on its own, its what happpens when you hide during battle<br>
<br>
<u>How to evade</u><br>
During a fight turn off attack, press hide, and then turn attack back on<br>
<br>
Note:  It is important that you not be moving or getting hit when you try to evade. so if the monster is beating on you, wait until he attacks, then evade between his swings.<br>
evade is useless while soloing. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugyorg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gyorg</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/8/02 2:13:30 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/5/02 9:37:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> #8 Skills: Pick Locks... </span><hr size=1> <b>Question:</b>  How do I raise/use Picklocks?<br>
