<B>Answer:</B>  You may pick any lock equal to or less than your picklock skill.<br>
You may NOT pick doors with a value higher than your level.<br>
<HR><br>
#27b<br>
<b>Question:</b>  How can I raise my picklock skill?<br>
<b>Answer:</b>  You may raise your picklock skill on any door you can pick.  You can NOT raise your skill on doors you cannot pick. It is not shown that Pick Lock goes up faster by opening higher level doors.  Also see post #13.<br>
